snippet.title: SmashKarts Official Trailer - A multiplayer deathmatch arena style game with Karts.
snippet.description:
Play at: https://smashkarts.io/join/trailer

Smash Karts is a 3D driving game where the objective is to collect power-up boxes and survive using whatever you find in them: Bullets, grenades, even rockets?! 

Buckle up, put on your hat, reload your guns and eliminate your opponents! You can even customise your kart! 

Can you last longer than all your playmates in this crazy, action-filled Mario Kart-like battle game?
